      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Purging Hatred",
        "Client": "Suspicious Shamanka",
        "Description": "*channeling* There exists a creature\r\nburning with hatred that stalks the\r\nfrozen hell searching for souls to\r\nconsume. For its sins, it must be...\r\n\u0022purified.\u0022 I will prepare the ritual to\r\ncleanse its spirit, you release the\r\nbeast from its mortal coil!",
